\u2212, and further, \u03b32\n\n\u00b1 = q\u2020q + qq\u2020 = 1, and they mutually anticommute with\n\n11\n\neach other {\u03b3+, \u03b3\u2212} = 0. If we define a Fock state", "embedding": [-0.0036905883, 0.0036998661, 0.0132423965, 0.011550688, 0.026952226, -0.025763623, 0.017735768, -0.0042999634, -0.074369095, 0.07412838, 0.018107194, -0.01829486, 0.030768067, -0.020160377, -0.034026314, -0.002171015, -0.012210815, 0.0034055605, -0.09504252, 0.026373038, 0.024965316, 0.003899925, -0.0296126, -0.019923668, -0.024973514, 0.037767686, 0.02427063, 0.031385444, 0.031444207, 0.055757344, 0.024503086, -0.017907025, 0.01872703, -0.02533354, 0.017182965, 0.0419311, -0.0078712385, -0.032900628, 0.043980017, -0.017114734, 0.06711224, -0.0035100267, 0.009345652, -0.0036534246, -0.032142263, 0.012828121, -0.049941685, 0.023371903, -0.02126465, -0.070979275, 0.00030504007, -0.0041440465, 0.039016485, -0.005974583, -0.015371247, -0.0043047643, -0.0011615988, 0.0047020945, -0.017953176, -0.039820958, 0.021734374, -0.020982493, 0.017798478, -0.049924746, 0.017696273, 0.05354909, 0.02097734, 0.06656142, -0.020028362, -0.021083856, -0.0044194157, 0.008714741, -0.023182768, -0.007861368, -0.040367175, 0.0016814386, -0.003780933, -0.0358037, -0.05840962, -0.035263486, 0.004496937, 0.008521425, -0.0034227706, 0.025506712, -0.0042068316, -0.0009830275, -0.021158801, -0.00041858596, -0.018585244, 0.0010375271, 0.03631449, 0.05865019, -0.025283054, 0.006090414, 0.0465392, 0.03183573, -0.00939038, 0.041170817, 0.021428145, -0.0048338766, 0.010045177, 0.08314136, -0.021210963, 0.053328034, -0.045640353, 0.03507369, -0.012354472, 0.011897846, -0.0137615735, -0.049125813, 0.026718633, -0.00932899, 0.007411712, 0.03602997, -0.022558354, 0.026409652, 0.031373475, -0.015287917, -0.044309426, -0.016628595, -0.016507348, -0.012493325, 0.04463856, 0.012232934, -0.040714733, -0.02617923, 0.021658003, 0.03846781, -0.0036395665, 0.0030758614, 0.0045505846, 0.0330311, 0.027023507, 0.042038172, -0.05